- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the challenges of implementing Continuous Experimentation on cyber-physical systems. 
- cs.EM (Emerging Technologies) is relevant as the paper discusses a new technique (Continuous Experimentation) being applied to the automotive industry. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper briefly mentions safety concerns related to implementing Continuous Experimentation on automotive cyber-physical systems.
